---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// Enable static generation for this page
export const prerender = true;
---



<Layout title="Community Impact">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img 
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517457373958-b7bdd4587205?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" 
        alt="Maine community" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/90 to-primary/70"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto py-24 px-4 sm:py-32 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        50 Years of Community Impact
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-white max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Since 1973, Quirk Auto Group has been more than just a car dealership. We're a proud member of Maine communities, dedicated to making a difference in the lives of our neighbors.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Timeline Section -->
  <div class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary sm:text-4xl">Our Journey Through the Years</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
          Five decades of growth, community service, and making Maine a better place.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-px h-full w-0.5 bg-gray-200"></div>
        
        <!-- 1973 -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-primary bg-white z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">1973</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-5/12 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">1973: The Beginning</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Jack Quirk Sr. purchases his first dealership, Bangor Chrysler Plymouth, marking the beginning of Quirk Auto Group's commitment to Maine communities.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 1977 -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">1977: Expanding Our Reach</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Acquisition of Darling's Chevrolet Oldsmobile in Bangor, establishing a multi-franchise presence and deepening our community roots.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-primary bg-white z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">1977</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 1982 -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-primary bg-white z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">1982</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-5/12 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">1982: Growing Together</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Opening of Quirk Chevrolet in its current location on Hogan Road, introducing innovative community programs and support initiatives.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 1991 -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">1991: New Generation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Jack Quirk Jr. and Bob Quirk join the family business, bringing fresh perspectives and expanding community involvement through youth sports and education programs.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-primary bg-white z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">1991</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2003 -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-primary bg-white z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">2003</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-5/12 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">2003: Auto Park Vision</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Development of Quirk Auto Park begins, creating a centralized location for multiple brands and establishing a major community hub in Bangor.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2008 -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">2008: Coastal Expansion</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Expansion to Belfast and Rockland, bringing our community-focused approach to Maine's coastal communities and supporting local initiatives.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-primary bg-white z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">2008</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2015 -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-primary bg-white z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">2015</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-5/12 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">2015: Southern Maine Growth</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Expansion into Portland and Augusta markets, introducing new community partnerships and charitable initiatives throughout southern Maine.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2023 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">2023: Celebrating 50 Years</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Marking half a century of serving Maine communities with 18 locations, over 1,000 employees, and millions in community contributions through sponsorships and donations.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-primary bg-white z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">2023</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Impact Stats -->
  <div class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary sm:text-4xl">Our Impact in Numbers</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
          50 years of making a difference in Maine communities
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">18</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">Locations Across Maine</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">1000+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">Maine Jobs Created</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">$10M+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">Community Contributions</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">500+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">Organizations Supported</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Community Testimonials -->
  <div class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary sm:text-4xl">Community Voices</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
          Hear from the organizations and people we've worked with over the years
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" 
              alt="Sarah Johnson" 
              class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <div class="font-semibold text-primary">Sarah Johnson</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Youth Sports Director</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            "Quirk Auto Group's support has been instrumental in growing our youth sports programs. Their commitment to community development goes far beyond simple sponsorship."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" 
              alt="Mike Sullivan" 
              class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <div class="font-semibold text-primary">Mike Sullivan</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Local School Principal</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            "The educational initiatives supported by Quirk have made a real difference in our students' lives. Their dedication to education is truly commendable."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" 
              alt="Emily Chen" 
              class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"
            />
            <div class="ml-4">
              <div class="font-semibold text-primary">Emily Chen</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Community Organization Leader</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            "For decades, Quirk Auto Group has been a pillar of support for local initiatives. Their impact on our community is immeasurable."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="bg-primary">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:py-16 lg:px-8 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
        <span class="block">Ready to make an impact?</span>
        <span class="block text-secondary-light">Submit your community support request today.</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-8 flex lg:mt-0 lg:flex-shrink-0 space-x-4">
        <a
          href="/sponsorship-request"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-secondary hover:bg-secondary-light"
        >
          Request Sponsorship
        </a>
        <a
          href="/donation-request"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-cta hover:bg-red-700"
        >
          Request Donation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>